---
title: Harissa King Prawns on Cranberry Bulgur with Spinach and Baby Leaf Salad
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Harissa King Prawns on Cranberry Bulgur in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
